&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Secured Loans (desirable but not essential)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A performance-driven mindset, taking accountability for your targets that drive the right outcomes for our customers whilst taking our business forward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll provide a best-in-class customer experience, going over and above each time for our customers, ensuring their satisfaction and fostering long-term loyalty.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ll be busy, so you’ll need to be organised, managing multiple cases&lt;/li&gt;
