&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial Manager - ZA Marketplace&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a commercially-minded and analytically sharp Commercial Manager to help grow our Loans marketplace and deepen our partnerships across South Africa’s leading banks and lenders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll report into the Head of Commercial and play a pivotal role in shaping and executing the Loans vertical strategy, managing high-value partnerships, and owning the commercial performance of the vertical. You must be comfortable working cross-functionally with product, engineering, and marketing to drive forward initiatives that create value for both our nearly 7mn South African users and our lending partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact, high-ownership role within a small but ambitious team - one that operates like a start-up but is backed by a global brand serving nearly 27 million users. If you&#39;re energised by the intersection of data, partnerships, strategy and fintech innovation, and want direct accountability for revenue growth and commercial performance, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re looking for a structured role with a clear playbook and defined lanes, it isn&#39;t.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the commercial performance of the Loans vertical, including revenue growth and partnership performance of your lending partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead execution of the commercial strategy for the Loans vertical, with oversight from the Commercial Lead&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain deep relationships with our lending partners covering South Africa’s biggest banks and fintech lenders - understanding their goals and challenges to unlock long-term value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate commercial agreements with both new and existing partners, ensuring ClearScore captures appropriate value for the services we deliver&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use internal and external data to identify opportunities, track performance, and forecast impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead initiatives to improve the user experience and partner outcomes of the Loans Marketplace, working closely with product, engineering and marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritise commercial initiatives based on expected value to users, partners, and ClearScore revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must-haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in one or more of the following:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategy consulting; or&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fintech, consumer finance, banking, or B2B tech platform environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success in commercial or partner-facing roles - such as sales, account management, or business development, with direct ownership of revenue targets or commercial outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commercial negotiation skills and the ability to manage senior stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency using analysis, data platforms and Excel to extract insights, model outcomes, and support commercial decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to operate autonomously – self-assessing and directing priorities, driving key outcomes and managing a partner portfolio independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic and entrepreneurial mindset with a passion for problem-solving and innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice-to-haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in a high-growth or tech-driven environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to product or platform-driven commercial models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct exposure to Fintech or traditional lending sectors is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
